if (!requireNamespace('pacman', quietly=TRUE)) install.packages('pacman')
pacman::p_load(
            ## data manipulation
            readxl,
            dplyr,
            ## data analysis
            purrr, 
            tidyr, 
            broom,
            ## data visualization
            ggplot2,
            ggthemes,
            patchwork,
            kableExtra, 
            ## data exportation
            openxlsx
        )
dat <- readxl::read_xls("RESULTS_GENETICA-DOSAGEM_250521.xls",
                        sheet='Genetica e Dosagem',
                        col_types=c(rep('numeric', 6), 'skip',
                                    rep('numeric', 2), 'skip', 
                                    rep('numeric', 13), 'skip', 
                                    rep('numeric',  5)))

dat <- dat|>
    dplyr::rename(diasI='Dias de internamento',
                  diasI12='Id1_Dias internamento (<12=0)', 
                  diasI8='Id2_Dias de internamento (<8=0)',
                  obito='Id3_Óbito (0=não)',
                  diasS7='Id4_Dias_antes_sint (<7=0)',
                  il6='IL-6 (pg/mL)', 
                  infg='INF-g (pg/mL)')|>
    dplyr::mutate(dplyr::across(!c('il6', 'infg'), factor))

Análise descritiva

Aspectos clínicos

diasS7_0 <- paste(
    '7 ou menos dias de', 'sintomas antes do internamento', sep='\n'
)
diasS7_1 <- paste(
    'Mais de 7 dias de', 'sintomas antes do internamento', sep='\n'
)
dat1 <- dat|>
    dplyr::mutate(
               Óbito=dplyr::recode(obito, '0'='Não', '1'='Sim'),
               diasS7=dplyr::recode(diasS7, '0'=diasS7_0, '1'=diasS7_1),
               diasI8=dplyr::recode(diasI8, '0'='Não', '1'='Sim'), 
               diasI12=dplyr::recode(diasI12, '0'='Não', '1'='Sim')
           )
dat1|>
    ggplot(aes(y=diasI, fill=Óbito))+
    geom_bar(alpha=0.7)+
    facet_wrap(~diasS7)+
    geom_text(stat='count',
              aes(label=sprintf('%s (%.1f%%)',
                                after_stat(count),
                                after_stat(100*count/sum(count))
                                )),
              position=position_stack(0.5))+
    labs(x='Frequência', title='Dias de internamento')+
    theme_fivethirtyeight(base_size=14)+
    theme(axis.title.x=element_text(
              margin=unit(c(t=3, r=0, b=0, l=0), "mm")
          ))+
    scale_fill_fivethirtyeight()

bar_dias8 <- dat1|>
    ggplot(aes(y=diasI8, fill=Óbito))+
    geom_bar(alpha=0.75)+
    facet_wrap(~diasS7)+

              aes(label=sprintf('%s (%.1f%%)',
                                after_stat(count), 
                                after_stat(100*count/sum(count))
                                )),
              position=position_stack(0.5))+
    labs(x='Frequência', title='8 ou menos dias de internamento')+

          axis.title.x=element_text(

point_lm <-
    dat1|>
    ggplot(aes(x=il6, y=infg))+
    geom_point(size=2)+
    geom_smooth(method='lm', size=1.5, se=FALSE)+
    labs(title='IL-6 vs. INF-g')+
    theme_fivethirtyeight(base_size=14)
point2_lm <- 
    dat1|>
    ggplot(aes(x=il6, y=infg, color=Óbito))+
    geom_point(size=2, color='black')+
    geom_smooth(method='lm', size=1.5, se=FALSE)+
    labs(title='IL-6 vs. INF-g')+
    theme_fivethirtyeight(base_size=14)+
    scale_color_fivethirtyeight()
(box_il6/box_infg/(point_lm|point2_lm))+
    patchwork::plot_layout(heights=c(1, 1, 3))

ttest <- purrr::possibly(t.test, otherwise=NA)
legenda <- paste(
    'Teste-t de Welch de duas amostras,',
    'bicaudal (hipótese alternativa)'

il6_diasS7 <- dat|>
    dplyr::select(diasS7, dplyr::starts_with('IL6'))
il6_diasI8 <- dat|>
    dplyr::select(diasI8, dplyr::starts_with('IL6'))
il6_diasI12 <- dat|>
    dplyr::select(diasI12, dplyr::starts_with('IL6'))
il6_obito <- dat|>
    dplyr::select(obito, dplyr::starts_with('IL6'))

il6_names <- dat|>
    dplyr::select(dplyr::starts_with('IL6rs'))|>
    names()

7 ou menos dias de sintomas antes do internamento

il6_diasS7_results <- 
    purrr::map(il6_names,
           ~il6_diasS7|>
               dplyr::group_by_at(.x)|>
               tidyr::nest()|>
               dplyr::mutate(
                          fit=purrr::map(data, ~ttest(il6~diasS7, .x)),
                          glanced=purrr::map(fit,
                                             purrr::possibly(
                                                        broom::glance,
                                                        otherwise=NA))
                      )|>
               tidyr::unnest(glanced)|>
               dplyr::select(!c(fit, parameter, method, alternative))
           )|>
    purrr::set_names(il6_names)%>%
    dplyr::bind_rows(., .id='marcador')|>
    tibble::as_tibble()|>
    dplyr::mutate(
               dplyr::across(dplyr::starts_with('IL6rs'), as.numeric), 
               )|>
    dplyr::mutate_at(
               dplyr::vars(dplyr::starts_with('IL6rs')),
               ~replace(., is.na(.), 0)
           )|>
    dplyr::mutate(genótipo=rowSums(
                      dplyr::across(dplyr::starts_with('IL6rs'))
                  ))|>
    dplyr::select(!c(dplyr::starts_with('IL6rs'), glanced))|>
    dplyr::relocate(genótipo, .after=marcador)|>
    dplyr::relocate(estimate, .after=estimate2)|>
    dplyr::relocate(statistic, .after=conf.high)|>
    dplyr::relocate(p.value, .after=statistic)

il6_diasS7_results <- il6_diasS7_results|>
    mutate(nobs=purrr::map_int(
                           seq(nrow(il6_diasS7_results)),
                           ~nrow(il6_diasS7_results$data[[.x]])
                       )
           )|>
    dplyr::select(!data)|>
    dplyr::relocate(nobs, .after=genótipo)

il6_diasS7_results|>
    kableExtra::kbl(caption=legenda, digits=4)|>
    kableExtra::kable_paper(
                    'hover', 'responsive', full_width=FALSE,
                    font_size=17.5
                )|>
    kableExtra::row_spec(
                    c(1, 3, 5, 7:9, 12, 15, 18:19, 21, 23, 25, 27),
                    bold=TRUE, color='white', background='#D7261E'
                )

infg_diasS7_results <- 
    purrr::map(infg_names,
               ~infg_diasS7|>
                   dplyr::group_by_at(.x)|>
                   tidyr::nest()|>
                   dplyr::mutate(
                              fit=purrr::map(data,
                                             ~ttest(infg~diasS7, .x)),
                              glanced=purrr::map(fit,
                                                 purrr::possibly(
                                                            broom::glance,
                                                            otherwise=NA))
                          )|>
                   tidyr::unnest(glanced)|>
                   dplyr::select(!c(fit, parameter, method, alternative))
               )|>
    purrr::set_names(infg_names)%>%
    dplyr::bind_rows(., .id='marcador')|>
    tibble::as_tibble()|>
    dplyr::mutate(
               dplyr::across(dplyr::starts_with('INFGrs'), as.numeric), 
               )|>
    dplyr::mutate_at(
               dplyr::vars(dplyr::starts_with('INFGrs')),
               ~replace(., is.na(.), 0)
           )|>
    dplyr::mutate(genótipo=rowSums(
                      dplyr::across(dplyr::starts_with('INFGrs'))
                  ))|>
    dplyr::select(!c(dplyr::starts_with('INFGrs'), glanced))|>
    dplyr::relocate(genótipo, .after=marcador)|>
    dplyr::relocate(estimate, .after=estimate2)|>
    dplyr::relocate(statistic, .after=conf.high)|>
    dplyr::relocate(p.value, .after=statistic)

infg_diasS7_results <- infg_diasS7_results|>
    mutate(nobs=purrr::map_int(
                           seq(nrow(infg_diasS7_results)),
                           ~nrow(infg_diasS7_results$data[[.x]])
                       )
           )|>
    dplyr::select(!data)|>
    dplyr::relocate(nobs, .after=genótipo)
